data.description: Fully updated Midcentury home in the heart of Central Tacoma. Exposed-beam vaulted ceilings, floor-to-ceiling windows, hardwood floors, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, new sod, fencing & landscaping, complete with brick fireplaces indoors & out. This home was meticulously remodeled to meet the rigorous standards required by FHA rehab loans & has been artfully completed to preserve mid-century charm with modern amenities. This updated beauty boasts 2 living/family rooms, 3 bedrooms, an office space with private entry, extensive cabinetry, closet & storage space throughout. Upstairs, you’ll find tranquility in the private primary suite with a full ensuite bathroom, an abundance of natural light, vaulted ceiling & 4 closets.
